<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrī śakavaruṣaṁbulu 1310 gunēṁṭi caitra kṛṣṇa tritīyanu guruvāra
<lb n="2" break="no"/>nanu maṁgipūṁḍi mumaḍināyaṁḍu tanaku Abhīṣṭārttasidigānu śrīna
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rasiṁhyanāthuniki nityamunnu koluvanu kolupulu patinokaṁḍu samarppiṁ
<lb n="4" break="no"/>cenu mēgāpu ciṁgunāyuni vaśānanu stōtrapāṭanibhaṁdhaṁ Okaṭi
<lb n="5"/>tiruvājāmaAvasaramaṁdunu divā ni<unclear>ba</unclear>ṁdhaṁ 1 Apamanāyaka AU
<lb n="6" break="no"/>bhaḷivaśānanu kurmmanaṁbyaḷavaśānannu tirumajyanaAvasaramaṁdu
<lb n="7"/>tirumajanagaraya 1 śrītulaśimāḷalu reṁḍu tiruvajamuAvasara
<lb n="8" break="no"/>maṁdu dēvināyaka gōpinātanāyuḍulu Ā<supplied reason="omitted">la</supplied>vaṭṭa nibaṁdhaṁ 1 I Avasaramaṁdu
<lb n="9" break="no"/>nu vallabhanaṁbyaḷu goḍaU niba<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>dhaṁ 1 dupaAvasaramaṁdu cāmarani
<lb n="10" break="no"/>baṁdhaṁ 1 <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> mēgapu<unclear>vaśana</unclear> diva nibaṁdaṁ 1 kurumanaṁbyaḷu diva 1
<lb n="11"/>tiru<supplied reason="omitted">ma</supplied>jana Avasaramaṁdu Ajapareḍi tevāsani koḍuku Anaṁtadāsiki saṁkī
<lb n="12" break="no"/>rtananibaṁdaṁ 1 Iṁduku prasadaṁ kuṁca kurmmanaṁbhyaḷacētanu ṭavupaṭi peṭitimi <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> 
